                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 content-item" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
                    <span>05</span>
                    <h4>Set your budget</h4>
                    <p>Enter your daily or lifetime budget, and the time period which you want your ads to run. (Eg-03 days or 7 days) These limits mean that you'll never spend more than you're comfortable with.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 content-item" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
                    <span>06</span>
                    <h4>Select your audience</h4>
                    <p>Based on your requirements, we choose your audience – such as age, location and other details – choose the demographics, interests and behaviors that represent your audience at its best.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 content-item" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
                    <span>07</span>
